{
  "stem": "19895.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 113.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because they knew themselves that there is no food for us, so how can these people march on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some guards were sympathetic to some degree.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some guards were horrible and just enjoying brutality and, and, and creating fear.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Arrow Cross usually, mostly, and always German commanding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they didn't introduce themself to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "None, none, I didn't know a soul.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the, on the belly of the boots, on, on, on nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we-- on the football field, in the, in the ground, pouring rain, in mud, next to railroad tracks on the railroad station, and always surrounded by these guards.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They themself didn't have a good time, I'm sure, because it was exhausting to march.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, but they had food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they, they were making sure that we are all there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how we arrived to a town called [HUNGARIAN], translation in English doesn't mean much.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's when we were turned over to German authorities. and we were put in two wagons-- animal transportation wagons, like they would deliver cows.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one of these wagons maybe took as many as 40, 60 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were practically no more room than standing up or, or, or just sitting down but holding yourself to the minimal amount of space.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the train took off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And from the cracks of the boarding of the wagons, we could see that we passed some towns.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we recognized that some of it was not no more Hungarian sights.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that trip in the wagons, again-- urine, feces, smell, odor, sickness, vomiting, death experienced for about a day and a half, going through locations.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "To our surprise, when we were taken out of the wagons, we found ourself in Hungarian territory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I will continue telling about that, as we go on.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
